{"tid":1741443,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Youtuber試圖不合理化示威者嘅言行舉止","createTime":"2019-11-20T10:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T10:54:14.000Z","uid":322203,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"efa371bcb85d97bda47a25ba70bece4ad8518c6e","tid":1741443,"uid":322203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Summary 喺下面</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=-L7lHWwnxsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3D-L7lHWwnxsc&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=05a3c59f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=-L7lHWwnxsc</a><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅論點<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 滑波謬誤</span></strong><br />\n示威者誇大逃犯條例嘅possible consequences嚟抹黑條例、用同樣手法抹黑禁蒙面法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 倒果為因</span></strong><br />\n示威者犯法係因，驚賊執法係果，如果唔犯法，驚賊就冇必要執法。<strong>我真係好想知呢條友係咪瞓咗五個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 二分法</span></strong><br />\n示威者將所有事黑白化，睇做非黑即白。示威者認為唔支持自己嘅就係敵人，但係其實社會上面有好多唔同意見，，而非非黑即白。示威者打住民主嘅旗號，就應該接受其他聲音<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4. 抹黑及妖魔化</span></strong><br />\n示威者會人身攻擊異見者，並捏造事實去抹黑佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">5. 真相片段量少</span></strong><br />\n示威都開遮私了、示威者用刀、汽油彈，驚賊就可以用相同武力，示威者鬧、打、恐嚇表明立場嘅記者，干預新聞自由，同佢哋口中嘅民主產生矛盾<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">6. 暴徒都是警察</span></strong><br />\n因為驚力不足，所以驚賊係唔會做臥底，所以所謂嘅暴徒都係示威者而非驚賊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">7. 宗教式口號</span></strong><br />\n中央/基本法冇答應過會有雙普選，而林奠早已回應訴求，只係冇答應，而示威者不斷武力升級係勒索<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">8. 這樣比好嗎？</span></strong><br />\n管理國家並不容易，十四億人口一定有好人有壞人，唔應該誇大一啲事去同其他國家比較<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">9. 層遞式回覆</span></strong><br />\n示威者認為一個人唔符合某啲條件就冇權批評<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10. 各界可做的事</span></strong><br />\n其他國家仿效香港示威者去暴力表達訴求，其他國家啲人好快就會知道呢啲示威根本就唔和平，而係恐怖襲擊，應該停止暴力。中立同埋反對暴力嘅人應該投票同埋申請做陪審團，舉報不公嘅片段同埋資料。記者應該持平報道新聞，見到流緊血嘅警察同埋市民應該報道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我只係想問：你係咪瞓撚咗五個月？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ea42b45f2f21a77d3394a0de855d859ea03db331","tid":1741443,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"Twitter 任務 －－－ 感謝美國參議院！！！ （列表已更新）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741421</a>"},{"pid":"25b29309e6f6dd6c094ad83016586ed4abe37c6f","tid":1741443,"uid":322203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">瞓咗五個月？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"48e00e5a7dffc7fade6b4e6ad19ae3282666ca57","tid":1741443,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:41:39.000Z","msg":"輿論機器"},{"pid":"dace778a56e07b36b85ca5f183fb2fe7f2eea202","tid":1741443,"uid":61282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"記得唔好㩒入去"},{"pid":"001a067fd08668c8998bc83828c92e213069760e","tid":1741443,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>藍絲扮淺黃日本撚<br />\n唔好理<br />\n唔好禁<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c21befd0e698c76af63a64e9017d622b41ff5d5a","tid":1741443,"uid":52299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa371bcb85d97bda47a25ba70bece4ad8518c6e","tid":1741443,"uid":322203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r